Enchanted Botanicals - Modified Grapes
attributes.body: Modified Grapes is an Indica weed strain resulting from a cross between GMO and Purple Punch. This strain is favored by experienced cannabis consumers for its beautiful purple color and its flavors reminiscent of grape, berry, and honey. According to our customers, Modified Grapes is associated with effects like drowsiness, relaxation, and arousal. Consumers often turn to Modified Grapes to alleviate symptoms related to anxiety, stress, and insomnia.

attributes.name: AiroPod - Durban Poison - Sativa - .5g
attributes.body:
AiroPod Strain Series .5g Cartridge

• Strain Series

• Sativa

• Durban Poison

• Pure Distillate Oil

• Full Terpene Profile

• High Potency

 

The AiroPod cartridge is more than a stylish magnet, it’s the first vessel of its kind. The secured mouthpiece and filling septum minimize the possibility of leakage, something which has been a common issue among older model vaporizers. Considering that risk of accidental exposure, to children or pets for example, the AiroPod cartridge was built for safety as well as durability.

Free from a traditional wick and coil setup, AiroPod cartridges adopted ceramic reactor technology to serve as the heating element. Unmatched thermal precision ensures concentrates are always vaporized at the proper temperature. This preserves the flavor of concentrates and prevents them from burning. The silver-plated magnetic base makes exchanging cartridges a snap, while ensuring a solid connection every time.

attributes.body:
With a starting potency of well over 85% cannabinoids, the Elite cartridge is perfect for the moderate to seasoned cannabis enthusiast. This cartridge offers sweet orange notes from plant-derived terpenes. The orange flavor is distinct while a rich creaminess covers your palate with a deliciousness reminiscent of a Creamsicle on a hot summer day. 

 

These cartridges use medical-grade ceramic atomizers that provide low failure rates, even draw distribution, no burning taste, and more vapor delivered per draw.

attributes.body:
Introducing the Kullukush 1 gram Tank in the Tangie Banana strain from Multitude Manufacturing. This tank is filled with a premium filtered distillate with over 90 percent THC potency and infused with a custom blend of live and botanical terpenes. KulluKush tanks are designed to provide you with a convenient and enjoyable cannabis experience. It's the pinnacle of potency and quality with the Kullukush Tank in the high-end I-Krusher ceramic reservoir.

Known for its energizing, uplifting, and relaxing effects, this tank offers a delightful combination of sweet, skunky, citrus, and fruity flavors. With each puff, you'll experience a smooth and flavorful vapor that captures the essence of this popular strain.

attributes.body: Black Mamba is an indica-dominant hybrid strain known for its dark, dense buds and potent effects. It often has a sweet and earthy aroma with hints of spice. Black Mamba delivers a strong, long-lasting high, inducing deep relaxation, sedation, and a dreamy, introspective state.

attributes.name: GMO 2g All-In-One Vape
attributes.body: GMO, short for Garlic, Mushroom, and Onion, is an indica-dominant hybrid strain with a distinct and pungent aroma reminiscent of its name. It typically offers a combination of savory and earthy flavors. GMO is known for its potent effects, including deep relaxation, euphoria, and potential appetite stimulation.
